about:
Company Description by Thomasnet
Manufacturer of conveyor pulleys & rollers. A variety of pulleys including flat & crowned pulleys, heavy duty bulk handing drum pulleys, heavy wall pulleys, stainless steel pulleys & wing pulleys are available. Hex rollers are available in a wide variety of sizes, materials & shaft installations in carbon steel, galvanized steel or PVC materials. Specialty rollers & pulleys include aluminum, rubber built on shafts, flanged rollers & deflection wheels. Pulley & roller parts include shafting, hubs & bushings. Vulcanized lagging services are furnished for all types of pulleys. Pulleys are suitable for food processing, contract packaging, steel shafting, warehousing, distribution & baggage handling conveyor applications.
Company Description by Chantland-PVS Co., The Pulley Div.
Established in 1943, The Chantland Company has long been recognized as the world leader in unit handling and specialty pulleys and rollers. And for good reason. Pulleys and rollers are not just part of our product line. They are our ONLY business.

In fact, more than 200 quality-conscious employees  and all 140,000 square feet of our modern facility  are dedicated to the manufacture of conveyor pulleys24 hours a day.
